# Installation of GHC 8.4.2

## Installation Script

**ATTENTION - Currently this is the script to build GHC 8.4.2 DWARF **

~~~
# get distribution   
cd $HOME/Downloads  
wget https://downloads.haskell.org/~ghc/8.4.2/ghc-8.4.2-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz

tar xvfJ ghc-8.4.2-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz

cd ghc-8.4.2 

# install  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-8.4.2  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-8.4.2  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd ..  
rm -rfv ghc-8.4.2*
~~~

